416
00:19:12,910 --> 00:19:15,030
You old ferryman, say no more.

417
00:19:16,670 --> 00:19:17,470
Alright then.

418
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:19,670
If you insist on crossing the river at night

419
00:19:19,670 --> 00:19:21,670
