516
00:23:55,430 --> 00:23:55,990
Everyone

517
00:23:56,360 --> 00:23:57,960
please sit tight and hold on.

518
00:24:00,790 --> 00:24:02,590
I want to see what this whirlpool

519
00:24:02,740 --> 00:24:03,940
